1. *Lisice* su stajale pored vrata. (The handcuffs were standing next to the door.)
2. Policajac je stavio *lisice* na kriminalca. (The policeman put the handcuffs on the criminal.)
3. Kako si uspeo da se oslobodiš *lisica*? (How did you manage to free yourself from the handcuffs?)
4. Ona je bila uhapšena i odvedena u stanicu zbog nošenja *lisica* na javnom skupu. (She was arrested and taken to the station for wearing handcuffs at a public gathering.)
5. Moramo kupiti nove *lisice* za policiju. (We need to buy new handcuffs for the police.)
6. *Lisice* su bile tesne i neugodne. (The handcuffs were tight and uncomfortable.)
7. Kriminalac je uspeo da pobegne dok je policajac pokušavao da mu stavi *lisice*. (The criminal managed to escape while the policeman was trying to put handcuffs on him.)
8. Na sudu su ga vezali *lisicama* za sto. (They tied him to the table with handcuffs in court.)
9. U nekim zemljama, *lisice* se koriste kao simbol slobode. (In some countries, handcuffs are used as a symbol of freedom.)
10. Kada su videli policajce sa *lisicama*, ljudi su počeli da beže. (When they saw the policemen with handcuffs, people started to run away.)